% Contents of the data file toolbox%% dfopen    - open a data file and write session-begin marker% dfhead    - write session header to file, including subject code, %             timestamp, RNG seeds, etc.% dfvar     - write a variable to file as an embedded command% dfcmd     - write an embedded MATLAB command to file% dfcols    - write a name for each data column to file% dfline    - write a line of data to file% dfprintf  - write an arbitrary string to file% dfclose   - close a data file and write session-end marker% dfdebug   - set debug state, which determines whether data is simultaneously%             written to command window%% 11-Oct-98 (RFM)